 importance of =0Aprivate markets and giving a path forward for more of its=
 emerging talent. ...=0A=0AThe restructuring combines capabilities from the=
 bank=E2=80=99s financing group, =0Afinancial-sponsors coverage in investme=
nt banking, and coverage of private =0Aequity firms from its fixed-income a=
nd equities trading group, according to a =0Astatement Monday. The firm=E2=
=80=99s banking and asset-management arms have long worked =0Atogether to o=
ffer clients private loans and investment opportunities.=0A=0AThe restructu=
ring reflects Goldman=E2=80=99s desire to =E2=80=9Coperate at the fulcrum o=
f one =0Aof the most important structural trends taking place in finance,=
=E2=80=9D Chief =0AExecutive Officer David Solomon said in the statement.=
=0A=0A(Disclosure: I used to work at Goldman, in the financing group.) The =
Wall =0AStreet Journal <> notes:=0A=0AIt will include the financial-sponsor=
s team that provides investment-banking =0Aservices to private-equity firms=
, the global financing group that finds =0Ainvestors to provide capital for=
 deals and a big chunk of what the company =0Acalls its FICC financing team=
 that makes loans tied to collateral to other =0Alenders, including private=
-credit funds.=0A=0AIt is also creating a team within Capital Solutions tha=
t will focus on finding =0Aalternative sources of financing, especially for=
 its corporate clients. =E2=80=A6=0A=0AThe move is a bet by the firm that a=
 large amount of its growth will come from =0Aarranging financing, both by =
facilitating deals through its investment-banking =0Aarm and its asset-mana=
gement business and using its own money to make loans. =0AThe unit will als=
o offer other capital-markets services, including equity =0Aunderwriting.=
=0A=0AAnd from Goldman=E2=80=99s statement:=0A=0AOur One Goldman Sachs appr=
oach allows us to channel the growing synergies =0Abetween our clients in G=
lobal Banking & Markets (GBM) and those in Asset & =0AWealth Management (AW=
M). The combination of a preeminent corporate franchise =0Awith a globally =
scaled investing platform allows us to identify the most =0Acompelling oppo=
rtunities for our investing clients across private credit, =0Aprivate equit=
y and other assets. The ability to source these private asset =0Aopportunit=
ies provides both important capital for our banking clients and =0Aunique i=
nvestments for our asset and wealth management clients.=0A=0AYes, right, yo=
u have raised money from investors, and you have managers whose =0Ajob is t=
